{"tid":1611673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日港島有成Team 綠色瑩光帶出現 你地驚乜撚？","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:15:22.000Z","uid":66390,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"640c53a342e1b3cfc2b0b43198a9865409eadea0","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人地唔撚係鬼呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就算你覺得人地係鬼<br />\n你地都係衝去打尻佢地<br />\n而唔係走囉！</span><br />\n<br />\n4個月都來啦大佬<br />\n仲咁驚<br />\n成班半徑5-6米長咁圍住跑走<br />\n完全無人敢埋身！<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問啦<br />\n係咪以後見到差佬同鬼<br />\n都係咁走？<br />\n點救人？<br />\n<br />\n出來有差佬就一定<br />\n夜晚係港覺既人<br />\n自己諗下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有 <br />\n逆住方向咁叫「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n真係好撚柒<br />\n要叫就向金鐘方向 support大隊咁叫"},{"pid":"5bbdfb28df270af8c9fb2e63fa301d7e447252e9","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"*夜晚係港島"},{"pid":"99b3f3a1abae6819d20d7799715a5ea935d10f5a","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"出來面對啦香港人！"},{"pid":"7e26f302c00ddb945d4dbd956287baf00782c53e","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ea50df30a1dabcb6c6f63016358d455f7ad1debb","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:40:44.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9a438e493c78bb9ed582a79fc5f5a940245b0bf1","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ea2b0765b08cd730b9b2fa297a6c98ccf7b418b3","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"037e1c9083aed78e322e0d4dfec726169269dc8a","tid":1611673,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:49:40.000Z